c: 39
v: 5
t: "Iye adalenga kumwamba ndi dziko lapansi m’choonadi Iye amapanga usiku kuti uphimbe usana ndiponso amapanga usana kuti uphimbe usiku ndipo adalamula dzuwa ndi mwezi kukhala zopanda mphamvu. Chilichonse kumaenda mu msewu wakewake. Ndithudi Iye ndi wamphamvu, ndi wokhululukira nthawi zonse"